response.headline: UI-TARS: Free open-source alternative to ChatGPT Agent with mobile support and account integration capabilities
response.summary: UI-TARS is an underrated AI Agent open source project available on GitHub that offers ChatGPT Agent capabilities but more powerful and practical because it can use accounts where you're already authenticated. Created by TikTok/Bytedance, though users should be careful with account access.
